        {
            "title": "Baiya International Group acquires Starfish and its decentralized protocol, UpTop.Meme, on BNB Chain, as part of its Web3 strategy.",
            "id": "982633de-f768-48a6-b5dd-9518415622c1",
            "description": "On September 19, 2025, Baiya International Group Inc. (BIYA) announced that it has signed a Share Purchase Agreement with STARFISH TECHNOLOGY-FZE and its shareholders. This Agreement entails BIYA acquiring 100% of Starfish and its flagship platform, UpTop.Meme (UpTop), a decentralized liquidity protocol on BNB Chain. UpTop offers on-chain liquidity services for crypto-native digital assets, tokenized U.S. equities, and digital bonds, aiming to be a premier decentralized liquidity infrastructure globally. This acquisition is a significant step in BIYA's Web3 strategy. BIYA is a human resources technology firm utilizing its cloud-based platform for crowdsourcing recruitment and SaaS-enabled HR services, listed on Nasdaq under BIYA.",
